Prometheus exporter for OPNsense gateway metrics.

Runs a daemon that polls dpinger gateway monitor sockets and writes
Prometheus-format metrics to the node_exporter textfile collector
directory. Exports gateway status, round-trip time, standard deviation,
and packet loss for all configured gateways.

Metrics exported:
  opnsense_gateway_status        - numeric status (0=down, 1=up, 2=loss, 3=delay)
  opnsense_gateway_delay_seconds - round-trip time in seconds
  opnsense_gateway_stddev_seconds - RTT standard deviation in seconds
  opnsense_gateway_loss_ratio    - packet loss ratio (0.0-1.0)
  opnsense_gateway_info          - informational metric with status/monitor labels

WWW: https://github.com/brendanbank/opnsense-gateway-exporter
